{
  "stem": "4187.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And these-- these gendarmes started screaming at us, if you didn't shut up-- oh naturally, dirty, filthy Jews, you name it-- if you don't shut up, we'll-- we'll burn the barn down, with you in it.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, it was, if you don't shut up, we'll start shooting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we knew that they mean it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We knew that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We started to understand that we are not people anymore, that we're entirely in the hands of these monsters.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we didn't get anything to eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think, if I remember correctly, I certainly can't remember even getting any water at that stage.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was absolutely awful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were sitting on the floor, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was nothing else.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were just clinging to each other and-- and waiting to wake up, because it was just so horrendous.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "From-- even from the ghetto, which was still-- there was a bed, there was a table-- we were left alone.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We hardly saw any-- well, they were around, naturally.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we-- they didn't come up to you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There-- you know, there was nothing-- we had nothing to do with them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then, suddenly, from one second to another, we ceased to be human, literally ceased to be human.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, the night went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't sleep, of course, but night went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And next morning we were got up, and we went for another-- we-- we were taken further out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then-- then we were in-- we-- we came to some huge barracks, unused barracks, but we weren't taken inside.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were in the courtyard outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a huge machine gun facing us, right in front of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the same story, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you make any noise at all-- and-- and they meant it.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
